\F[3]\AA[F]Even though we haven't obtained all the codes yet...
we've been released!?
What a bunch of irresponsible people....

\F[3]\AA[F]Well, I was just at a dead end, so it's a good
thing... Oh, and there's a girl I want to introduce you to.
Because I've been released from prison after a long time.
addLog セリア「（それどころじゃなくない..？｝」

\F[10]\AA[F]Hold on, Hayato. Your priorities are all over the
place.

\F[10]\AA[F]Shouldn't escaping from this space be our first
priority?
........But we don't have any clues to the code, do we?
That's why I thought we might find a hint if I read the book.
\F[15]\AA[F]Is, is that so? But that was a fabrication....

Anyway, try consulting with that spirit about various things.
I'll do a little more investigating on my own.
\F[10]\AA[F](Something's been off for a while now...)

\F[10]\AA[F](...Wait, did I tell him that Ann is a spirit? I
wonder if he saw it from the prison.)
I've shown you us being lovey-dovey, Hayato♡
After all.. I can't do it, big sis♡ This kind of thing♡
You're not complaining, are you?♡ You love me, don't you?

Keep going like this and secretly find out what those guys are up
to, okay? My cute, cute \c[14]spy-kun\c[0]♡
'おねえちゃんの言う通りにすればまた気持ちよくしてもらえる...'
'"私達"にお任せください、サディ様..♡'

Spenia complete. After defeating the leader of the Orlind guard,
ask about the back door. Bariente is under Merill's jurisdiction.

\F[1]\AA[F]What do you expect me to do with this?
魔法使い報告セックス_1

Arrangements have been made to invade the town of Spenia in the
northwest with the army of succubi♡

The soldiers patrolling the town and the gatekeepers have already
been seduced♡♡
The pink-haired woman straddles Sadi... conveying something.

As expected of my servant...♡ But there were supposed to be many
female soldiers in Spenia. Was that okay?
Haah♡ Ahn♡.... Huh..?♡ Oh, of course...................

I made the women quarrel with each other using \c[27]Charm
(Fascination)\c[0]♡ It's my specialty after all♡♡

Hehehe... It's the best, isn't it♡ Then, let's give you a
reward♡♡

The succubus, who had been completely still until now, suddenly
begins to piston.
魔法使い報告セックス_2

You've changed quite a bit compared to \c[27]one year ago\c[0],
haven't you♡
Please continue to serve me faithfully, my servant....
Of course..♡ Everything is for the sake of \c[27]paradise\c[0]♡

Currently, on Ci-en, a mini-game is being developed that includes
situations that couldn't be included in the main story♡ Register
and see Celia and Hayato in their helpless state♡♡
\F[1]\AA[F]Ci..en? I don't understand that first. It's nonsense.
